OL,5,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FYorkshire's A&E struggles with too
OL,7,     Fmany patients and not enough room
OL,8,     Ffor them as they work to treat
OL,9,     Finternal chest wounds, a collapsed
OL,10,     Flung and a back injury.
