OL,5,G2200 A&E After Dark
OL,6,     FIn Newham, a boy, 19, lies with a
OL,7,     Fpotentially broken neck after a
OL,8,     Fjudo match - any movement could
OL,9,     Fworsen his injury. Meanwhile,
OL,10,     Fdoctors fight to save a patient
OL,11,     Fwith a collapsed lung.
OL,12,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FDr Toby is spellbound by his
OL,14,     Fpatient, Gideon, Preston's
OL,15,     Fpart-time witch, and Dr Natalia
OL,16,     FSpierings tries to help a young
OL,17,     Fwoman with a scalp condition
OL,18,     Fusually found in middle-aged men.
